Cosmos;;1996;;NC;;Comedy,Drama;;6.6;;Jennifer Alleyn,Manon Briand,Marie-Julie Dallaire;;Marie-Hélène Montpetit,Pascal Contamine,France Castel,Marie-France Lambert,Alexis Martin,Stéphane Crête,Martin Neufeld,Marjolaine Huard,Colette Courtois,Renée Girard,Annie Laroche,Martin Morel,Sebastien Joannette,Eve Gadouas,André Forcier,Patricia Groleau,Mireille Naggar,Élise Guilbault;;Through an immigrant cab driver, our world collides with a nervous filmmaker, a lawyer whose new breasts her ex-boyfriend wants to see, a mystery man, a gay man who may or may not be HIV-positive, and a birthday girl who got stood up. It is a mixture of laughter and sadness, all floating on a sea of philosophy.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0118889/